Approximately body length: 18.0; head width: 
<number box="[1009,1047,1054,1079]" pageId="2" pageNumber="83" value="5.7">5.7</number>
; inter-tegular span: 
<number box="[1281,1319,1054,1079]" pageId="2" pageNumber="83" value="6.3">6.3</number>
; forewing length: 16.0; UID: 
<number box="[373,425,1090,1115]" pageId="2" pageNumber="83" value="2.35">2.35</number>
; LID: 
